            "title": "Dietary overlap and seasonality in three species of mormoopid bats from a tropical dry forest",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Valeria B.",
                    "lastName": "Salinas‐Ramos"
                },
                {
