            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Investigations on Vector-Borne and Aerosol Transmission Potential of Kaeng Khoi Virus in Cave-Dwelling Wrinkle-Lipped Free-Tailed Bats (Chaerephon plicatus) in Thailand",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "William A.",
